  3.30  1.0  1.0    0.0  0.0  0.0
 SPHERICAL CUTOFF
  10.0
 KPOINTS MONKHORST-PACK
  16 16 16
 STATES
  9
&END

&ATOMS
*Nb-q5 KLEINMAN-BYLANDER RAGGIO=1.2
   LMAX=D LOC=P
   1
   0.00D0       0.00D0          0.00D0
&END
